text: Zdeněk Vávra (25 September 1891 - 18 September 1947) was an Olympic fencer who competed for Bohemia in 1912 and Czechoslovakia in 1920. ==References== Category:1891 births Category:1947 deaths Category:Czech male fencers Category:Olympic fencers of Bohemia Category:Olympic fencers of Czechoslovakia Category:Fencers at the 1912 Summer Olympics Category:Fencers at the 1920 Summer Olympics Category:Czechoslovak male fencers
